{"tid":2304632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：特朗普支持者賓夕法尼亞州挑戰大選結果遇挫折","createTime":"2020-11-29T03:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T08:53:46.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"28fbf8beb8e382865ca194a3c19a506e44fcf60d","tid":2304632,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國總統特朗普支持者循法律挑戰大選結果再遇到挫折。<br />\n</strong><br />\n共和黨人向賓夕法尼亞州最高法院入稟，要求裁定郵寄選票無效，或者推翻州的投票結果，由州議會決定勝選人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法院的裁決一致駁回兩項要求，認為要法院剝奪在大選中投票的690萬名州選民的權利是非比尋常的主張。</strong><br />\n<br />\n最高法院又認為，入稟人挑戰州議會去年通過一項容許居民郵寄選票是違反州憲法，已經為時已晚，因為法案頒布超過一年，而大選結果亦似乎顯而易見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562599-20201129.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562599-20201129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=92aadbd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562599-20201129.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=867ecbc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562599-20201129.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c1441ea43f419550269d4ca792dfe5cff84bb316","tid":2304632,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c23c838ee22b82866b3e7703b6737e301f99cce","tid":2304632,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終都打唔低廢老登<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8274f31fc678426cf0bc33f4ee35a58068aec0fe","tid":2304632,"uid":241742,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T03:5